    'CM' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Ivugurura E-ubucuruzi muri Kameruni hamwe na Selldone Ubucuruzi OS</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Yongerera imbaraga Kumurongo wawe</h3>\r\n<p>Muri Kameruni, imbaraga zikomeye kumurongo zitangirana na nyirubwite. Hamwe na Selldone y'ubucuruzi OS, abacuruzi bo muri Kameruni barashobora kwihatira kwinjiza ibikorwa bya e-bucuruzi muri domaine zabo zisanzwe, bigatuma ibicuruzwa bihoraho kandi bigatera ikizere mubakiriya.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ubunararibonye bwo Gushiraho</h3>\r\n<p> Wibagiwe ingorane zo kugura hosting, kwishyura amacomeka, cyangwa gushungura inyandikorugero. Selldone itanga uburyo bworoshye bwo gushyiraho uburyo bwateganijwe ku isoko rya Kameruni, bituma abacuruzi bibanda ku bucuruzi bwabo bwibanze: kugurisha.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3> Kubara Imisoro Yukuri</h3>\r\n<p>Gusuzuma amategeko yimisoro muri Kameruni birashobora kuba ingorabahizi. Selldone Ubucuruzi OS ifite uburyo bwo kubara imisoro ihujwe neza n’ibipimo bya Kameruni, byemeza ko byubahirizwa kandi bisobanutse muri buri gikorwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Kubucuruzi bwa Kameruni bukomeye</h3>\r\n<p>Nubwo waba utangiye gukura cyangwa ikirango cyamenyekanye muri Kameruni, Selldone yagenewe gupima hamwe nibyifuzo byawe. Urwego rukomeye rushyigikira inzira yo gukura kwamasosiyete yihuta cyane, yemeza ko yita kubakiriya baguka.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Yakorewe kugurisha no Guhindura</h3>\r\n<p>Ibintu byose biri muri Selldone Ubucuruzi OS bwakozwe kugirango bongere urugendo rwabakiriya, gutwara ibinyabiziga no guhindura ibintu. Ntabwo ari urubuga rwa e-ubucuruzi gusa; ni dynamo yo kugurisha kubacuruzi bo muri Kameruni.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Gutera inkunga kubaguzi ba Kameruni</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b>Kode yo kubara</b> kwizihiza ibihe byiminsi mikuru nibihe bidasanzwe.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Exclusive itanga</b> ishimisha kandi ihemba abakiriya b'indahemuka.</li>\r\n    <li>Q<b>Cross-kugurisha no kugurisha</b> kugirango yongere agaciro gakomoka kubigura byose.</li>\r\n    <li><b> Impano yikarita iranga</b> itunganye kuri ibyo bihe bidasanzwe byimpano.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3> Kwamamaza ibicuruzwa byateganijwe kuri Kameruni</h3>\r\n<p>Gukoresha abanya Kameruni bisaba kumva neza ibyo bakunda. Selldone yubatswe mu kwamamaza no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza byoroshya umurimo wo guhuza, kwishora, no guhindura abakiriya bawe, byose mugihe bihujwe nisoko rya Kameruni.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Kuki Selldone ihagaze</h3>\r\n<p>Ibikorwa nka WooCommerce birashobora kuba byiza, ariko bizana ibibazo byihariye. Gukenera kwakira, hamwe na UI / UX idahwitse, birashobora kubuza benshi kwibira muri e-ubucuruzi. Selldone, bitandukanye, itanga uburambe bwubusa butarimo izo mbogamizi.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ihinduranya Imikorere gakondo ya E-ubucuruzi</h3>\r\n<p>Ibikorwa bisanzwe nka Guhindura, Salesforce, na Magento akenshi bisaba kwishyiriraho amacomeka menshi hamwe na templates. Hariho kandi ibyago byugarije byo gusangira amakuru yawe nabandi bantu hamwe nibishobora kugwa mumacomeka adakora. Selldone ikuraho ibyo bigoye, yerekana igisubizo kiboneye, gifite umutekano, kandi cyiza kubacuruzi bo muri Kameruni.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abacuruzi bo muri Kameruni bashaka gusobanura urugendo rwabo rwa e-bucuruzi, Selldone Business OS nigihe kizaza. Wibire kandi wibonere e-ubucuruzi nkubwa mbere.</p>"],
