    'DE' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Leading E-commerce Transformation in Germany with Selldone Business OS</h2>\n\n<p>In the heart of Germany, where innovation meets tradition, Selldone Business OS is redefining the e-commerce landscape. This no-plugin platform is tailored to meet the unique needs of German merchants, offering a comprehensive solution to sell products, services, subscriptions, and even files.</p>\n\n<h3>Stake Your Digital Claim</h3>\n<p>German businesses can now elevate their online presence. With Selldone, e-commerce is seamlessly integrated into your own domain, ensuring authenticity and a direct connection with every visitor.</p>\n\n<h3>Unparalleled Simplicity</h3>\n<p>Launching an online storefront in Germany should be straightforward. Selldone ensures that merchants can embark on their e-commerce journey with ease, eliminating the intricacies of hosting, plugins, and templates.</p>\n\n<h3>Aligned with Germany's Tax System</h3>\n<p>Understanding the nuances of Germany's tax regulations, Selldone integrates a comprehensive tax calculation feature. This ensures that businesses operate smoothly, adhering to local taxation norms without complications.</p>\n\n<h3>Engineered for Ambitious German Brands</h3>\n<p>From startups in Berlin to established brands in Munich, Selldone is designed to scale and evolve. It's the e-commerce ally for businesses with a vision, ready to grow.</p>\n\n<h3>Optimized for Sales Excellence</h3>\n<p>Selldone isn't merely about selling; it's about excelling. Crafted with the German market in mind, it's fine-tuned to convert visitors into loyal customers.</p>\n\n<h3>Engaging Incentives for the German Shopper</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b> to celebrate and reward.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b> to enthrall a diverse audience.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> to maximize the shopping experience.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> for those cherished moments.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing Tailored for Germany</h3>\n<p>Engaging the German audience is effortless with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. It's about forging lasting connections in the heart of Europe.</p>\n\n<h3>Redefining E-commerce Standards</h3>\n<p>While platforms like WooCommerce might present challenges with hosting and a fragmented user experience, Selldone offers a cohesive and intuitive journey for both merchants and shoppers.</p>\n\n<h3>Surpassing Traditional Platforms</h3>\n<p>Conventional e-commerce platforms, such as Shopify, Salesforce, or Magento, often come with their set of challenges:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Risks</b> due to third-party sharing.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> that can disrupt the seamless shopping flow.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> with a myriad of plugins and templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone simplifies this, offering German merchants a streamlined, secure, and efficient e-commerce experience.</p>\n\n<p>For the merchants of Germany, Selldone Business OS is the future of e-commerce. Dive in and experience the next level of online business.</p>\n"],
