    'DK' => ['footer_note' => "<h3>Ivugurura E-ubucuruzi muri Danimarike hamwe na Selldone Ubucuruzi OS</h3>\n\n<p>Ku bacuruzi batekereza imbere muri Danimarike, ahazaza h'ubucuruzi harahari. Selldone Ubucuruzi OS yerekana urubuga rwa e-ubucuruzi rudafite icyerekezo, nta-plugin ruhuza ibikenewe bidasanzwe hamwe n’ibidukikije by’ubucuruzi bwa Danemark. Waba ugurisha ibicuruzwa, serivisi, abiyandikisha, cyangwa dosiye, Selldone yagutwikiriye.</p>\n\n<h3>YUbucuruzi bwawe E-Ubucuruzi, Domisiyo yawe</h3>\n<p> Hamwe na Selldone, abacuruzi bo muri Danemark barashobora kwishimira umwanya wabo wa digitale. Urubuga rwose rwa e-ubucuruzi rwakiriwe kurubuga rwawe bwite, rwemeza guhuza ibicuruzwa no kwizerwa.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibidafite gahunda kubacuruzi bo muri Danemark</h3>\n<p> Wibagiwe ingorane zo kugura hosting cyangwa gukoresha kumacomeka na templates. Selldone itanga inzira yoroshye yo gushiraho, yemerera ubucuruzi muri Danimarike kwibanda kubyo bakora byiza: kugurisha.</p>\n\n<h3>Byuzuye Kubara Imisoro Kubara</h3>\n<p>Kumva neza uburyo bwimisoro ya Danemark, Selldone ije ifite ibikoresho byo kubara imisoro bigenewe igihugu, byemeza ko byubahirizwa nta ngorane.</p>\n\n<h3>Ku bicuruzwa byihuta-byihuta bya Danemark</h3>\n<p>Selldone ntabwo ari kubitangira gusa. Yashizweho kubunini, bituma ihitamo neza kumasosiyete yaguka byihuse nibirango byerekana ibicuruzwa muri Danimarike.</p>\n\n<h3>Yakorewe kugurisha no Guhindura</h3>\n<p>Ibintu byose muri Selldone bikozwe ufite intego imwe: kuzamura ibicuruzwa byawe. Kuva mubishushanyo mbonera byacyo kugeza kubakoresha-bifashisha, byose ni ukwemeza ihinduka ryinshi kubacuruzi bo muri Danemark.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibitera Galore</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Kode</b>: Tanga ibiciro byihariye kubakiriya b'indahemuka.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibyifuzo byihariye</b>: Kureshya abakiriya bashya bafite amasezerano yigihe gito.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Igurisha na Upsells</b>: Ongera agaciro ka buri gikorwa.</li>\n    <li><b> Impano Ikarita Yimpano</b>: Reka abakiriya bawe basangire urukundo.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Ibikorwa byo Kwamamaza no Kwamamaza</h3>\n<p>Komeza mbere yaya marushanwa hamwe na Selldone yubatswe mu kwamamaza no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza. Shikira abakwumva bo muri Danemarike neza kandi neza, urebe ko bahorana impamvu yo kugaruka.</p>\n\n<h3>Kubera iki Selldone Ihagaze muri Danemark</h3>\n\n<h3> Ugereranije na WooCommerce</h3>\n<p>Mu gihe WooCommerce isaba kwakira kandi akenshi igaragaza uburambe-butari bwiza bwabakoresha, Selldone itanga urubuga rworoheje, rworohereza abakoresha. Ntabwo uzongera gutura kuri subpar UI / UX.</p>\n\n<h3> Inyungu Zirenze Imiyoboro gakondo ya E-ubucuruzi</h3>\n<p>Ibikoresho nka Guhindura, Salesforce, na Magento akenshi bisaba kwishyiriraho amacomeka menshi hamwe na templates. Ibi ntibigora gusa uburambe bwabakoresha ahubwo binatera ingaruka: </p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Kugabana</b> hamwe nabandi bantu birashobora guhungabanya umutekano wubucuruzi bwawe.</li>\n    <li><b> Amacomeka yamenetse</b> arashobora guhagarika ibikorwa byawe bya e-bucuruzi.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibibazo</b> irashobora kubuza abakiriya no kugabanya ibicuruzwa.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> Hamwe na Selldone, abacuruzi bo muri Danemarike barashobora kwishimira uburambe bwubucuruzi bwa e-bucuruzi, butekanye, kandi bunoze.</p>\n\n<h3>Emera ahazaza ha E-ubucuruzi muri Danemark</h3>\nIgihe cya <p>Igihe cyabacuruzi bo muri Danemarke batera imbere mugihe kizaza hamwe na Selldone Business OS. Inararibonye itandukaniro ryurubuga rwateguwe ukeneye ibyo ukeneye.</p>"],
