    'GB' => ['footer_note' => "<h2> Guhindura E-ubucuruzi kubacuruzi bo mubwongereza hamwe na Selldone Ubucuruzi OS</h2>\n\n<p> Mu mutima w’amasoko yuzuye y’Ubwongereza, hagaragaye ibihe bishya bya e-ubucuruzi. Selldone Business OS, urubuga rwa e-ubucuruzi rudafite plugin, rurimo gushiraho urwego rwabacuruzi mu gihugu hose. Kuva ku bicuruzwa kugeza kuri serivisi, kwiyandikisha kuri dosiye, ibintu byose ubu birashoboka. </p>\n\n<h3>Own Umwanya wawe wa Digital</h3>\n<p> Abacuruzi mubwongereza ubu barashobora kwishimira kwerekana ituro ryabo kurubuga rwabo bwite. Ntibizongera kumvikana, gusa ibirango byera no kwizera.</p>\n\n<h3>Ubunararibonye bwo Gushiraho</h3>\n<p> Wibagiwe tekiniki ya jargon nurutonde rutagira iherezo rwibisabwa. Gushiraho hamwe na Selldone numuyaga. Ntabwo ari ngombwa gucengera mu kwakira ibintu bigoye cyangwa gukoresha amafaranga yinyongera kuri plugin na templates. Byose bijyanye n'ubworoherane no gukora neza.</p>\n\n<h3>Ubwongereza-Biteguye Kubara Imisoro</h3>\n<p> Hamwe no gusobanukirwa byimazeyo sisitemu yimisoro yu Bwongereza, Selldone itanga uburyo bwuzuye bwo kubara imisoro. Kubahiriza ntibikiri akajagari ahubwo ni inzira igororotse.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibirango kuri Rise</h3>\n<p> Ubundi uri intangiriro igaragara cyangwa ikirango cyamenyekanye mubwongereza, umunzani Selldone hamwe nawe. Yubatswe mukuzamura, kwemeza ko uhora utera imbere.</p>\n\n<h3>Yateganijwe kubihinduka ntarengwa</h3>\n<p>Ibintu byose bya Selldone byakozwe kugirango bahindure abashyitsi abakiriya. Ntabwo ari kugurisha gusa; ni kugurisha ubwenge.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibikorwa Bitera</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Kode</b> guhemba abakiriya b'indahemuka.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibyifuzo byihariye</b> kugirango ushukishe abumva bashya.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Igurisha na Upsells</b> kugirango yongere agaciro k'ibikorwa.</li>\n    <li><b> Impano Ikarita Yimpano</b> kuri ibyo bihe bidasanzwe.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Ubucuruzi bwamamaza Magic</h3>\n<p> Hamwe na Selldone yubatswe mu kwamamaza no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza, kugera kubateze amatwi icyongereza ntabwo byigeze bikora neza. Nibyerekeye gukora amahuza aramba.</p>\n\n<h3>Kuki Selldone ihagaze</h3>\n<p>Mu gihe urubuga nka WooCommerce rutanga uburambe butandukanye hamwe no gukenera kwakira hamwe na UI / UX idahwitse, Selldone itanga urugendo ruhuriweho, rworohereza abakoresha.</p>\n\n<h3>Gutambuka Kurenga Amahuriro gakondo</h3>\n<p>Ibikoresho bisanzwe bya e-ubucuruzi, byaba Guhindura, Salesforce, cyangwa Magento, biza hamwe nibibazo byabo bwite: </p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Byamakuru</b> kubera gusangira nabandi bantu.</li>\n    <li><b> Amacomeka yamenetse</b> ihagarika imikorere yoroshye.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibikoresho Byuzuye</b> hamwe namacomeka menshi hamwe na templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone ikuraho izo mbogamizi, itanga uburambe bworoshye kubacuruzi bo mubwongereza.</p>\n\n<p>Igihe kirageze kubacuruzi bo mubwongereza bakira ejo hazaza ha e-ubucuruzi hamwe na Selldone Business OS. Urubuga rwumva neza ibyo ukeneye.</p>"],
