    'IN' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Ivugurura E-ubucuruzi kubacuruzi bo mubuhinde hamwe na Selldone Ubucuruzi OS</h2>\n\n<p>Mu masoko akomeye yo mubuhinde, aho umuco uhura nudushya, Selldone Business OS itangiza ibihe bishya bya e-ubucuruzi. Iyi porogaramu idafite plugin yagenewe abacuruzi bo mu Buhinde, itanga inzira idafite aho igurisha ibicuruzwa, serivisi, abiyandikisha, ndetse na dosiye.</p>\n\n<h3> Shiraho uburyo bwawe bwa Digital</h3>\nUbucuruzi bwa <p>Indiyani burashobora gukora umwanya wihariye kuri enterineti. Hamwe na Selldone, urubuga rwa e-ubucuruzi ruba kumurongo wahisemo, ukemeza isano nyayo nabashyitsi bose.</p>\n\n<h3>Intangiriro zitoroshye</h3>\n<p>LGutangiza iduka rya interineti mubuhinde ntibigomba guhuzwa nibibazo. Selldone iremeza ko abadandaza bashobora gushiraho bitagoranye, bivanaho gukenera kwakira, amacomeka, cyangwa inyandikorugero. Nukugirango e-ubucuruzi butaziguye kandi bworoshye.</p>\n\n<h3>Yubahiriza Sisitemu yimisoro yo mubuhinde</h3>\nImiterere yimisoro ya <p>India iragoye, ariko Selldone irahari kubikorwa. Hamwe nimiterere yo kubara imisoro ihuriweho, iremeza ko ubucuruzi bugendana nu misoro yimisoro yaho bitagoranye.</p>\n\n<h3>Gushushanya hamwe nubucuruzi bukomeye bwu Buhinde</h3>\n<p> Kuva mubitangira muri Bengaluru kugeza ibicuruzwa byashizweho i Mumbai, Selldone yagenewe gutera imbere hamwe nubucuruzi bwabahinde. Numufatanyabikorwa wa e-ubucuruzi kubafite icyerekezo.</p>\n\n<h3>Ihinduka kuri Core</h3> yayo\n<p>Selldone ntabwo igurishwa gusa; nibijyanye no gukoresha amahirwe yose. Yakozwe ku isoko ryu Buhinde, ni byiza guhindura abashyitsi abakiriya b'indahemuka.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibikorwa byo Gutanga Umuguzi wu Buhinde</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Kode</b> kwizihiza ibirori byo guhaha iminsi mikuru.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibyifuzo byihariye</b> kugirango bashimishe abahinde batandukanye bo mubuhinde.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Igurisha na Upsells</b> kugirango uzamure agaciro ka buri gare.</li>\n    <li><b> Impano Ikarita Yimpano</b> kuri ibyo bihe bidasanzwe byimpano.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Ubucuruzi bwamamaza kubuhinde bwabahinde</h3>\n<p>Kugera kubantu benshi mubuhinde kandi batandukanye ni umuyaga hamwe na Selldone yubatswe mumamodoka n'ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza. Nibyerekeye gushiraho ubumwe burambye muri demokarasi nini kwisi.</p>\n\n<h3>Gusobanura ibipimo bya e-ubucuruzi mubuhinde</h3>\n<p>Mu gihe urubuga nka WooCommerce rushobora kwerekana imbogamizi hamwe no kwakira hamwe nuburambe bwabakoresha, Selldone itanga urugendo ruhuriweho kandi rwihuse kubacuruzi n'abaguzi.</p>\n\n<h3> Kurenga Amahuriro gakondo</h3>\n<p>Ibikoresho bisanzwe bya e-ubucuruzi, nka Guhindura, Salesforce, cyangwa Magento, akenshi bizana nibibazo byabo: </p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Ibibazo Byamakuru</b> kubera kugabana kwabandi.</li>\n    <li><b> Amacomeka yamenetse</b> ashobora guhungabanya uburambe bwo guhaha.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibikoresho Byuzuye</b> hamwe namacomeka menshi hamwe na templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone yoroshya ibi, itanga abacuruzi bo mubuhinde urugendo rworoshye, rwizewe, kandi rwiza rwa e-ubucuruzi.</p>\n\n<p> Kubacuruzi bo mubuhinde, Selldone Business OS ntabwo irenze urubuga gusa; ni ejo hazaza h'ubucuruzi. Wibire kandi wibonere itandukaniro.</p>"],
