    'PH' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Gushushanya E-ubucuruzi Ejo hazaza muri Philippines hamwe na Selldone Ubucuruzi OS</h2>\n\n<p>Muri Philippines, aho amasoko akomeye ahura nudushya, Selldone Business OS irimo gukora inzira nshya kubucuruzi bwa e-bucuruzi. Iyi porogaramu idafite plugin yagenewe abacuruzi bo muri Filipine, ibafasha kugurisha ibicuruzwa bitandukanye, serivisi, abiyandikisha, ndetse na dosiye byoroshye.</p>\n\n<h3>Carve Digital yawe Niche</h3>\n<p>Ku bucuruzi bwa Filipine, gushiraho indangamuntu idasanzwe kumurongo ubu biroroshye kuruta mbere hose. Hamwe na Selldone, e-ubucuruzi bwinjiza muburyo bwihariye wahisemo, byemeza ukuri no kwizerana nabashyitsi bose.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibikoresho bitagira umupaka kubacuruzi bo muri Filipine</h3>\n<p>LGutangiza iduka rya interineti muri Philippines bigomba kuba akayaga. Selldone iremeza ko abacuruzi bashobora gushyiraho urusaku ruke, bikuraho gukenera kwakira, amacomeka, hamwe na templates. Byose bijyanye no gukora e-ubucuruzi bworoshye kandi bworoshye.</p>\n\n<h3>Yifatanije na sisitemu yimisoro ya Philippines</h3>\n<p> Hamwe no gusobanukirwa byimazeyo imisoro ya Philippines, Selldone itanga uburyo bwo kubara imisoro. Ibi byemeza ko ubucuruzi buguma bwubahiriza mugihe bugenda bugora imisoro yaho.</p>\n\n<h3>Gupima hamwe na Filipine Ibyifuzo</h3>\n<p> Kuva mubitangira i Manila kugeza ibicuruzwa bikura muri Cebu, Selldone yagenewe guhinduka hamwe nawe. Numufatanyabikorwa mwiza wa e-ubucuruzi kubucuruzi butekereza iterambere no gutsinda.</p>\n\n<h3>Ihinduka-Hagati Yegereye</h3>\n<p>Selldone ntabwo ari kugurisha gusa; ni ukureba amahirwe yose abara. Yakozwe hamwe nisoko rya Filipine mubitekerezo, nibyiza guhindura abashyitsi kuba abakiriya b'indahemuka.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibikorwa byo Gutangiza Abaguzi ba Filipine</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Kode</b> kwishimira no guhemba abakiriya b'indahemuka.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibintu byihariye</b> kugirango ushukishe abantu benshi.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Igurisha na Upsells</b> kugirango igure byinshi mubikorwa.</li>\n    <li><b> Impano Ikarita Yimpano</b> kuri ibyo bihe bidasanzwe byimpano.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Ibicuruzwa byamamaye byateganijwe kuri Philippines</h3>\n<p>Guhuza abanya Filipine batandukanye biragoye hamwe na Selldone yubatswe mumamodoka n'ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza. Nibyerekeye kubaka amasano arambye muri archipelago.</p>\n\n<h3>Gusobanura ibipimo bya e-ubucuruzi</h3>\n<p>Mu gihe urubuga nka WooCommerce rushobora kwerekana ibibazo hamwe no kwakira hamwe nuburambe bwabakoresha, Selldone itanga urugendo ruhuriweho kandi rworohereza abakoresha kubacuruzi n'abaguzi.</p>\n\n<h3> Kurenga Amahuriro gakondo</h3>\n<p>Ibikoresho bisanzwe bya e-ubucuruzi, nka Guhindura, Salesforce, cyangwa Magento, biza hamwe nibibazo byabo: </p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Ibibazo Byamakuru</b> kubera gusangira nabandi bantu.</li>\n    <li><b> Amacomeka yamenetse</b> ashobora kubangamira uburambe bwo guhaha.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibikoresho Byuzuye</b> hamwe na plugin na templates zitabarika.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone yoroshya ibi, itanga abacuruzi bo muri Filipine urugendo rworoshye, rwizewe, kandi rwiza rwa e-ubucuruzi.</p>\n\n<p>Ku bacuruzi bo muri Philippines, Selldone Business OS yerekana ahazaza h'ubucuruzi. Wibire kandi wibonere umurongo ukurikira wubucuruzi kumurongo.</p>"],
    'PK' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Gushushanya E-Ubucuruzi bushya Era muri Pakisitani hamwe na Selldone Ubucuruzi OS</h2>\n\n<p>Mu masoko yuzuye no guhindura imibare ya Pakisitani, Selldone Business OS irimo gukora icyuho mubucuruzi bwa e-bucuruzi. Iyi porogaramu idafite plugin yateguwe neza kubacuruzi bo muri Pakisitani, itanga igisubizo cyuzuye cyo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byinshi, serivisi, abiyandikisha, ndetse namadosiye.</p>\n\n<h3>Carve Digital yawe Niche</h3>\n<p>Pakistani ubucuruzi ntibukigarukira kumipaka yumubiri. Hamwe na Selldone, e-ubucuruzi bwinjiza muburyo bwihariye wahisemo, byemeza ukuri kandi bigatera ikizere hamwe nabashyitsi bose kumurongo.</p>\n\n<h3>Intangiriro Yintangiriro</h3>\n<p> Gutangiza umushinga wo kumurongo muri Pakisitani bigomba kuba bidafite ibibazo. Selldone iremeza ko abacuruzi bashobora gutangira urugendo rwabo rwa e-ubucuruzi byoroshye bitagereranywa, bakuraho ibibazo byo kwakira, amacomeka, hamwe na templates.</p>\n\n<h3>Yahurijwe hamwe n’imisoro yo muri Pakisitani</h3>\n<p> Hamwe no gusobanukirwa kwimiterere yimisoro ya Pakisitani, Selldone ihuza uburyo bukomeye bwo kubara imisoro. Ibi bituma ubucuruzi bukora nta nkomyi, bwubahiriza amahame yimisoro yaho nta nkomyi.</p>\n\n<h3>Gushushanya hamwe na Brake ya Visionary Marks</h3>\n<p> Kuva mubitangira kugaragara i Karachi kugeza ibicuruzwa byateye imbere i Lahore, Selldone yitiriwe gukura hamwe. Numufatanyabikorwa wa e-ubucuruzi kubucuruzi buteganya ejo hazaza .</p>\n\n<h3>Ihinduka-Hagati Yegereye</h3>\n<p>Selldone irenze kugurisha gusa; nibijyanye no guhitamo amahirwe yose ashoboka. Yakozwe hifashishijwe isoko rya Pakisitani, hubahwa guhindura abashyitsi mubakiriya bitanze.</p>\n\n<h3>Ibikorwa byo Gutangiza Abaguzi bo muri Pakisitani</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Ibisobanuro Kode</b> kwizihiza ibirori byo guhaha iminsi mikuru.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibyifuzo byihariye</b> kugirango ushukishe abumva batandukanye.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Igurisha na Upsells</b> kugirango wongere uburambe bwo guhaha.</li>\n    <li><b> Impano Ikarita Ikiranga</b> kuri ibyo bihe byiza byimpano.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Ibicuruzwa byamamaza Byashizwe muri Pakisitani</h3>\n<p>Gukoresha abanya Pakisitani batandukanye kandi bafite imbaraga ni cinch hamwe na Selldone yubatswe mumasoko n'ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza. Nibyerekeye guhimba amasano arambye muri iki gihugu gifite imbaraga.</p>\n\n<h3>Gushiraho Ubucuruzi bushya bwa E-ubucuruzi</h3>\n<p>Mu gihe urubuga nka WooCommerce rushobora kwerekana ibibazo hamwe no kwakira no gutanga ubunararibonye bwabakoresha, Selldone itanga urugendo ruhuriweho kandi rworohereza abakoresha kubacuruzi n'abaguzi.</p>\n\n<h3>Guhindura uburyo bwa gakondo</h3>\n<p>Ibikoresho bisanzwe bya e-ubucuruzi, nka Guhindura, Salesforce, cyangwa Magento, akenshi biza guhura nibibazo: </p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Ibibazo Byamakuru</b> kubera gusangira nabandi bantu.</li>\n    <li><b> Amacomeka yamenetse</b> ashobora guhungabanya urugendo rwo guhaha nta nkomyi.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibikoresho Byuzuye</b> ikenera amacomeka menshi hamwe na templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone yoroshya ibi, itanga abacuruzi bo muri Pakisitani uburambe bwa e-ubucuruzi bworoshye, butekanye, kandi bunoze.</p>\n\n<p>Ku bacuruzi bo muri Pakisitani, Selldone Business OS ntabwo ari urubuga gusa; ni umuseke wigihe gishya cya e-ubucuruzi. Tangira uru rugendo kandi usobanure neza ubucuruzi bwawe kumurongo.</p>"],
