ango ushukishe abakiriya batandukanye.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Igurisha na Upsells</b> kugirango uzamure uburambe bwo guhaha.</li>\n    <li><b> Impano yikarita Ikiranga</b> kuri ibyo bihe bidasanzwe byo gushimira.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Ibicuruzwa byamamaza Byashizwe muri Singapore</h3>\n<p>Guhuza abumva isi yose muri Singapuru ntagahato hamwe na Selldone yubatswe mumamodoka n'ibikoresho byo kwiyamamaza. Nibyerekeye kubaka amasano yumvikana.</p>\n\n<h3>Gusobanura ibipimo bya e-ubucuruzi</h3>\n<p>Mu gihe urubuga nka WooCommerce rushobora kwerekana imbogamizi hamwe no kwakira hamwe nuburambe bwabakoresha, Selldone itanga urugendo ruhuriweho kandi rworohereza abakoresha kubacuruzi ndetse nabaguzi.</p>\n\n<h3> Kurenga Amahuriro gakondo</h3>\n<p>Ibikoresho bisanzwe bya e-ubucuruzi, nka Guhindura, Salesforce, cyangwa Magento, akenshi bizana nibibazo byabo: </p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Ibibazo Byamakuru</b> kubera gusangira nabandi bantu.</li>\n    <li><b> Amacomeka yamenetse</b> ashobora kubangamira uburambe bwo guhaha nta nkomyi.</li>\n    <li><b>Ibikoresho Byuzuye</b> hamwe na plugora nyinshi hamwe na templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone yoroshya ibi, itanga abacuruzi bo muri Singapuru urugendo rworoshye, rwizewe, kandi rwiza rwa e-ubucuruzi.</p>\n\n<p>Ku bacuruzi batekereza imbere muri Singapuru, Selldone Business OS nigihe kizaza cya e-ubucuruzi. Wibire kandi wibonere ubwihindurize imbonankubone.</p>"],
